name: 145,161 Mints
description: 2000x2000 video. A visualization of the first 145,161 Mints on Hic et Nunc arranged chronologically from the bottom left to the top right, where height corresponds to the number of editions that were minted. Data collected using http://hicdex.com/. Original artwork by landlinesart (twitter: @landlinesart1 instagram: @at_landlinesart)
